snippet.title: Sblobber 64 - Homebrew game for the N64
snippet.description:
Gameplay for sblobber 64 on the N64. This is the runner-up for the 2020 64brew game jam. To find out more and download the ROM, visit N64Squid: https://n64squid.com/sblobber-64/

This is my attempt at a speedrun, beat in 1m51s. It's a bit hard to control since the character's movement is a bit slippery which is why I sometimes stop to take my time.
